{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"04f58c8f32","title":"丘勤宝的右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ba5f115934","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"04f58c8f32"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1adb8d6260","name":"丘勤宝"},{"id":"4c0546f58a","name":"成都工学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d0060ca7c1","type":"title","text":"丘勤宝的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"04f58c8f32"},{"id":"c51213bb37","type":"authors","text":"成都工学院丘勤宝","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"04f58c8f32"},{"id":"b4aa06bd38","type":"subtitle","text":"(丘勤宝：成都工学院教授)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"04f58c8f32"},{"id":"1478144b71","type":"paragraph","text":"“报纸上鼓吹农村劳动收入如何高，这样作不恰当，党对知识分子老是要改造学习，为什么不对工农提出改造呢？”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"04f58c8f32"},{"id":"72a00e041e","type":"paragraph","text":"“学校中的人可分三种：一为领导的话唯命是听，这被称为是进步分子，但心里想的，不得而知；二为不反对看风色的，被认为中间分子，而有话直说的，被算为顽固分子。知识分子有自尊心，有些意见，平时被记下来汇报上去，到运动时就整一番，这甚至伤了别人的人格。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"04f58c8f32"},{"id":"7b84d83e0e","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《右派言论选集》（中共成都工学院委员会办公室，1957年）。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"04f58c8f32"}],"page":{"id":"b12323c131","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"04f58c8f32","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}